earch Council shall appoint the members of the Legislature including at least one member from each party from both the Senate and the House of Representatives. Section 3. The Department of Education shall report its findings and recommendations to the Executive Board of the Legislature Research Council no later than December 1, 2008."}], "amendments": [], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 5034, "action_date": "2008-01-16T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 1254, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/1254.pdf", "status_text": "First read in House and referred to", "journal_page": 155, "committee_id_action": 27, "committee_id_assigned": 16, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 5034, "action_date": "2008-02-05T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 2309, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/2309.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for hearing", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 16, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 5034, "action_date": "2008-02-05T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 2532, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/2532.pdf", "status_text": "Do Pass", "journal_page": 413, "committee_id_action": 16, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {"vote_id": 1258, "president_vote": null, "Yea": [609, 625, 580, 537, 599, 559, 564, 565], "Nay": [608, 534, 595, 620, 566], "Excused": [630, 611]}}, {"bill_id": 5034, "action_date": "2008-02-06T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 2642, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/2642.pdf", "status_text": "Deferred to another day", "journal_page": 443, "committee_id_action": 27, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 5034, "action_date": "2008-02-07T13:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 2758, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/2758.pdf", "status_text": "Deferred to another day", "journal_page": 468, "committee_id_action": 27